      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in concours condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been professionally overhauled. Power is delivered via a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. Crucially, the chassis has undergone preventative subframe reinforcement, and rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells for long-term reliability. The suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed bushings and factory-spec dampers. Clad in original paint with zero orange peel or rock chips, and an interior devoid of bolster wear, this is a mechanically flawless example for the purist collector.",
